~ chapter2_star_fragment

Star Fragment: Welcome, Blessed One.

Player: ...

Player: You were waiting for me?

Star Fragment: For a very long time.

Star Fragment: I am Hiraya,
Star Fragment: the Star of Peace.

Star Fragment: Though my light was imprisoned,
Star Fragment: peace endured because you carried it within your heart.

Player: Then...

Player: You'll be joining the others?

Star Fragment: Gladly.

Star Fragment: My journey now lies with yours.

Star Fragment: Come closer.

Star Fragment: Let my light become one with your own.

=> END


